Class SSPSinglesTrigger

  • java.lang.Object

  • public class SSPSinglesTrigger
extends SSPNumberedTrigger
    Class SSPSinglesTrigger represents a singles trigger reported by the SSP and also handles the parsing of the trigger data.

        Instantiates a new SSPSinglesTrigger object.
        Parameters:
        isTrigger0 - - Indicates whether this is the first or second of the singles triggers.
        isTop - - Indicates whether this trigger was thrown by the top or the bottom SSP crate.
        time - - Indicates at what time the trigger occurred in ns.
        data - - The raw trigger data associated with this trigger.
